        "description": "<p><em>EA Mahjong</em> is a tile matching game using Mahjong tiles laid out in one of 72 patterns called horoscopes. Players must click on two matching tiles to clear them from the board, making sure to select tiles in play (ones not sandwiched between other tiles). Once one horoscope is cleared, the player can continue to the next one. Controls use the wheel, to slide between tiles which can be removed.</p>\n<p>The single-player mode involves playing on any of these 72 layouts, at your leisure. The Emperor's Challenge has 12 levels with tough time limits - beat them all to unlock a final level. Multiplayer is supported via the Press 'N' Play mode - see who can clear a certain layout first.</p>",
